{"id":319228,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/10/冯学荣-《隐动力》之冯玉祥的120万小洋钱/","date":"2013-10-22T09:02:18Z","modified":"2013-10-22T09:02:18Z","title":"冯学荣 | 《隐动力》之冯玉祥的120万小洋钱","content":"<p><p><span>“中国近代史发展到节骨眼的时候，发挥关键作用的，往往不是什么高尚的主义，而是赤裸裸的金钱。” －<br />\n《隐动</span><span>力：中国</span><span>历</span><span>史中的金</span><span>钱</span><span>游</span><span>戏</span><span>》</span><span>连载</span><span>作者</span> <span>冯</span><span>学荣 自序</span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p ALIGN=\"center\">\n<span>《隐动</span><span>力》之</span><span>冯</span><span>玉祥的</span><span>120<span>万小洋</span></span><span>钱</span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p ALIGN=\"center\">\n<span>冯</span><span>学荣</span></p>\n<p ALIGN=\"center\">\n<span> </span></p>\n<p ALIGN=\"center\">\n<span> </span></p>\n<p><span>         <br />\n1924<span>年，爆</span></span><span>发</span><span>了</span><span>“<span>第二次直奉</span></span><span>战</span><span>争</span><span>”<span>。</span></span><span>张</span><span>作霖和段祺瑞、</span><span>孙</span><span>中山</span><span>结</span><span>成“三角</span><span>联</span><span>盟”、</span><span>对</span><span>付吴佩孚。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n         </span><br />\n<span>这场</span><span>“<span>第二次直奉</span></span><span>战</span><span>争</span><span>”<span>的来</span></span><span>龙</span><span>去脉，是怎么回事呢？</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n         <br />\n<span>我</span></span><span>们</span><span>先来听听</span><span>历</span><span>史</span><span>见证</span><span>人曹汝霖，是怎么</span><span>说</span><span>的：</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n        <br />\n“…&#8230;.<span>自从在第一次直奉</span></span><span>战</span><span>争当中</span><span>战败</span><span>之后，</span><span>张</span><span>作霖回到沈阳，整</span><span>军</span><span>改革，准</span><span>备</span><span>雪耻</span><span>……&#8230;</span><span>这时</span><span>在南方，原本同属革命</span><span>阵营</span><span>的粤</span><span>军</span><span>和桂</span><span>军</span><span>交</span><span>恶</span><span>、</span><span>继</span><span>而开打，</span><span>孙</span><span>中山在广州不能安居。</span><span>这时则</span><span>出</span><span>现</span><span>了</span><span>“<span>段祺瑞、</span></span><span>张</span><span>作霖、</span><span>孙</span><span>中山三角</span><span>联</span><span>盟</span><span>”<span>、</span></span><span>联</span><span>合</span><span>对</span><span>抗直系</span><span>军阀</span><span>曹</span><span>锟</span><span>、吴佩孚</span><span>……..</span><span>时</span><span>机成熟，</span><span>张</span><span>作霖果断出兵，以</span><span>“</span><span>讨</span><span>伐</span><span>贿选</span><span>”</span><span>为</span><span>由，攻打曹</span><span>锟</span><span>。奉</span><span>军</span><span>从山海关入关。直</span><span>军则</span><span>并分三路迎</span><span>战</span><span>，王</span><span>怀庆</span><span>、胡景翼</span><span>为</span><span>中路，</span><span>冯</span><span>玉祥</span><span>为</span><span>北路，吴佩孚</span><span>则驻</span><span>秦皇</span><span>岛</span><span>，自任</span><span>总</span><span>指</span><span>挥</span><span>…….<span>不料，在关</span></span><span>键</span><span>的</span><span>时</span><span>刻，</span><span>冯</span><span>玉祥和段祺瑞、</span><span>张</span><span>作霖互通款曲、收受了</span><span>张</span><span>作霖、段祺瑞的巨款</span><span>贿赂</span><span>，从</span><span>怀</span><span>来（京郊的一个</span><span>县</span><span>）突然倒戈，第二天就</span><span>杀</span><span>入北京。同</span><span>时</span><span>，直</span><span>军</span><span>在山海关、九</span><span>门</span><span>口都打了</span><span>败</span><span>仗。至此，第二次直奉</span><span>战</span><span>争，奉系</span><span>胜</span><span>出</span><span>……..<span>”</span></span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span>（参香港春秋</span><span>杂</span><span>志社，曹汝霖《一生之回</span><span>忆</span><span>》</span><span>1966<span>年</span>1<span>月初版，第</span>244<span>－</span>246</span><span>页</span><span>）</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n            <br />\n<span>曹汝霖短短几百字的描述，已</span></span><span>经</span><span>在大体上</span><span>讲</span><span>明白了</span><span>“<span>第二次直奉</span></span><span>战</span><span>争</span><span>”<span>的来</span></span><span>龙</span><span>去脉：</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n1<span>、第二次直奉</span></span><span>战</span><span>争，是第一次直奉</span><span>战</span><span>争的延</span><span>续</span><span>。</span><span>张</span><span>作霖在第一次直奉</span><span>战</span><span>争当中打</span><span>输</span><span>了，他不</span><span>认输</span><span>，卷土重来，</span><span>报</span><span>仇雪耻。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n2<span>、吴佩孚在</span>“<span>第二次直奉</span></span><span>战</span><span>争</span><span>”<span>中的失</span></span><span>败</span><span>，是因</span><span>为</span><span>吴佩孚的部下猛将</span><span>冯</span><span>玉祥的倒戈叛</span><span>变</span><span>，而</span><span>冯</span><span>玉祥的倒戈，并不是出于什么高尚的主</span><span>义</span><span>，而是因</span><span>为冯</span><span>玉祥收受了</span><span>张</span><span>作霖的</span><span>贿赂</span><span>。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n          <br />\n<span>那么，</span></span><span>张</span><span>作霖</span><span>给</span><span>了</span><span>冯</span><span>玉祥多少</span><span>钱</span><span>？我</span><span>们</span><span>来听听当年在北洋政府</span><span>陆军</span><span>部任</span><span>职</span><span>的</span><span>证</span><span>人王坦。王坦在不同的</span><span>场</span><span>合，亲耳听</span><span>见张</span><span>作霖自己</span><span>说</span><span>：</span><span>张</span><span>作霖</span><span>给</span><span>了</span><span>冯</span><span>玉祥“</span><span>120<span>万小洋</span></span><span>钱</span><span>”。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span>王坦</span><span>证</span><span>言一：</span><span>“……<span>（我）在</span></span><span>见</span><span>到</span><span>张</span><span>作霖</span><span>时</span><span>……</span><span>张</span><span>（作霖，</span><span>对</span><span>我）</span><span>说</span><span>：好吧，你回去</span><span>见</span><span>到曹三</span><span>爷</span><span>（曹</span><span>锟</span><span>），替我安慰他几句，没什么，</span><span>别</span><span>看打仗，我</span><span>俩还</span><span>是朋友，</span><span>冯</span><span>玉祥替咱打仗，那是</span><span>120<span>万小洋</span></span><span>钱买</span><span>他的，他不能主持国事，以后在北京有事情，可以跟李景林、</span><span>张</span><span>学良他</span><span>们联络</span><span>……”</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span>（参中国文史出版社《我所知道的北洋三雄》</span><span>2004<span>年</span>1<span>月第</span>1<span>版，第</span>142</span><span>页</span><span>）</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span>王坦</span><span>证</span><span>言二：</span><span>“……1925<span>年夏初</span>……<span>我又去了沈阳，</span></span><span>张</span><span>作霖</span><span>请</span><span>我吃</span><span>饭</span><span>，并</span><span>对</span><span>我</span><span>说</span><span>：</span><span>“………</span><span>冯</span><span>玉祥</span><span>这</span><span>小子</span><span>说话</span><span>没信用，一派奸</span><span>诈</span><span>……<span>他是冲着咱</span>120<span>万小洋</span></span><span>钱</span><span>，你当他真心与我合作么？吴佩孚是</span><span>败</span><span>了，吴佩孚要是</span><span>胜</span><span>了，他（</span><span>冯</span><span>玉祥）</span><span>还</span><span>不是打我么？</span><span>……”</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span>（参中国文史出版社《我所知道的北洋三雄》</span><span>2004<span>年</span>1<span>月第</span>1<span>版，第</span>143</span><span>页</span><span>）</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n          <br />\n<span>依据王坦的</span></span><span>证</span><span>言，</span><span>张</span><span>作霖分</span><span>别</span><span>在两个不同的</span><span>场</span><span>合，</span><span>对</span><span>王坦</span><span>亲</span><span>口透露了自己</span><span>给</span><span>予</span><span>冯</span><span>玉祥“</span><span>120<span>万小洋</span></span><span>钱</span><span>”</span><span>贿赂的事实</span><span>。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n          <br />\n<span>那么，“</span>120<span>万小洋</span></span><span>钱</span><span>”大概是多少</span><span>钱</span><span>呢？我</span><span>们</span><span>来看看</span><span>东</span><span>沟</span><span>县（今辽东省东</span><span>港市</span><span>）</span><span>文化</span><span>馆老</span><span>干部、生于</span><span>1918<span>年的</span></span><span>赵</span><span>云国的回</span><span>忆</span><span>：</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span>“（九一八之前）</span><span>英国人</span><span>见</span><span>从大</span><span>东</span><span>沟到沙河子交通不便，就弄来一条汽船，从大</span><span>东</span><span>沟到沙河子来往拉客，船脚每人小洋</span><span>钱</span><span>五毛。汽船</span><span>这</span><span>玩</span><span>艺</span><span>儿跑得快，三四个</span><span>钟头</span><span>就到了。</span><span>”</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n          <br />\n<span>可见，在与第二次直奉战争相近的年代里，搭乘</span>3<span>、</span>4<span>个小时的汽船，只需要花小洋钱五毛。那么，冯玉祥所接受的“</span>120<span>万小洋钱”贿赂，是个什么概念，大家应该心里有谱了。</span></span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n          <br />\n<span>当然，冯玉祥不会承认自己拿钱的事情。冯玉祥在自己的回忆录里面，是这样说的：</span></span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n           <br />\n“……</span><span>奉</span><span>军发动进</span><span>攻，兵分三路，直</span><span>军</span><span>也派兵三路、</span><span>进</span><span>行迎</span><span>战</span><span>，吴佩孚自己任第一路，沿着京奉</span><span>铁</span><span>路前</span><span>进</span><span>，王</span><span>怀庆</span><span>任第二路，出喜峰口，我（</span><span>冯</span><span>玉祥）任第三路，</span><span>经</span><span>由古北口</span><span>进</span><span>攻</span><span>热</span><span>河，吴佩孚交代胡笠僧：如果我</span><span>冯</span><span>玉祥有什么异</span><span>动</span><span>，</span><span>对</span><span>我就地解决，十分心毒。</span><span>这时</span><span>， 黄郛（同盟会背景，蒋介石的拜把子兄弟）和我有所</span><span>联络</span><span>。</span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span>          <br />\n<span>我到了古北口的时候，段祺瑞给我送信来，劝我止戈。张作霖也派了个代表马先生来劝我，说张作霖的目的在于打倒曹锟、吴佩孚，一旦他们倒台，绝不入关，我当时就对他说：我已经和北京几个将领接洽好了，只要你们奉军不入关，我就帮你们推翻曹锟、吴佩孚。我对他建议：推倒曹锟、吴佩孚之后，请孙中山先生来北京、主持国是，马先生说：没问题</span>..……</span><span>”</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span>（参冯玉祥《我的生活》上海教育书店</span><span>1947<span>年初版，第</span>497<span>－</span>505<span>页）</span></span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n           <br />\n<span>可见，冯玉祥自述的要点如下：</span></span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n1<span>、冯玉祥背叛自己的长官吴佩孚，是因为吴佩孚对自己不好。</span></span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n2<span>、冯玉祥倒戈，是段祺瑞和张作霖派人来游说的，没有钱的交易。</span></span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n         <br />\n  <span>事实上，冯玉祥收受张作霖的贿赂，不但有曹汝霖的说法、王坦的证言，还有更多的证人证言，如果要笔者列举的话，笔者可以列出几千字，出于篇幅考虑，笔者再带领大家看最后一条证人证言：张学良的证言。张学良是这么说的：</span></span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span>“我跟冯玉祥是拜把兄弟，冯玉祥倒戈完全跟我有很大关系，我给了他五十万块钱，那时候我们秘密勾结，谁也不知道。”</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n          <br />\n<span>张学良的这个证言，出自于唐德刚所著《张学良口述历史》第</span>63<span>页。当然，张学良说的“</span>50<span>万块钱”，和张作霖所说的“</span>120<span>万小洋钱”，也许是汇率的问题，也也许是张学良记忆的失误，还也许是张学良在张作霖的“</span>120<span>万小洋钱”之外，另外又给了冯玉祥“</span>50<span>万块钱”。但是，无论是哪一个版本，都并不影响以下这个事实的成立：冯玉祥是收了张家父子的钱。</span></span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n         <br />\n<span>可见，冯玉祥“收钱倒戈”的这个事情，恐怕是基本可以成立的了。</span></span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n          <br />\n<span>冯玉祥说自己倒戈是受了“国民革命”的熏陶，而背后的真相，却是因为收受了张作霖父子的钱财。如果张作霖父子当年不花这笔钱，中国历史又是什么样的走向呢？</span></span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p ALIGN=\"center\">\n<span>冯学荣</span> <span><br />\n2013<span>年</span>10<span>月</span>22<span>日，写于 中国 香港</span></span></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/special/1265.gif\" /> <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://sina.allyes.com/main/adfclick?db=sina&#038;bid=204720,469641,474922&#038;cid=0,0,0&#038;sid=473458&#038;advid=358&#038;camid=37389&#038;show=ignore&#038;url=http://qing.blog.sina.com.cn/tag/%E5%86%99%E7%9C%9F\">青春就应该这样绽放</a>  <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://sina.allyes.com/main/adfclick?db=sina&#038;bid=204720,469645,474926&#038;cid=0,0,0&#038;sid=473464&#038;advid=358&#038;camid=37389&#038;show=ignore&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Funion.9173.com%2Fpub%3Fp%3D1%26u%3D1008\">游戏测试：三国时期谁是你最好的兄弟！！</a>  <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://sina.allyes.com/main/adfclick?db=sina&#038;bid=204720,469646,474927&#038;cid=0,0,0&#038;sid=473465&#038;advid=358&#038;camid=37389&#038;show=ignore&#038;url=http://qing.blog.sina.com.cn/tag/%E6%98%9F%E5%BA%A7\">你不得不信的星座秘密</a><img src=\"http://sina.allyes.com/main/adfclick?db=sina&#038;bid=204720,470173,475454&#038;cid=0,0,0&#038;sid=474001&#038;advid=358&#038;camid=37389&#038;show=ignore&#038;url=http://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/common/sg_trans.gif?t=0\" /></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheet/embeddedform?formkey=dGRpN3FrVThuMFFsZHBZcmNGLW94dEE6MQ\" width=\"450\" height=\"309\" frameborder=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\">Loading&#8230;</iframe></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":1004,"categories":[18270,18269,9203],"tags":[9400]}